          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <node refid="T14" role="Change"/>
          <node refid="T13" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1239</offset>
        <text>Our results show that the canonical Redfield N:P ratio of 16 is not a universal biochemical optimum, but instead represents an average of species-specific N:P ratios.
</text>
      </sentence>
